snippet.textDisplay: FNAF was the most impactful game of the decade for me, and the most impactful game of my life. It opened up all of the possibilities for me, showed me the ability to begin YouTube, start fanfiction writing, and allow my mind to begin comprehending full storylines. I also don't get scared of jumpscares and gore anymore but that's beyond the point... I've become a great writer and an amazing thinker and have had amazing opportunities handed to me, all because of this game. FNAF has also brought me to meet some amazing people online, whether you may think it to be a good thing or not. FNAF has been very impactful on my life.
